2026-05-04T00:52:30.9119497Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-04T00:52:30.9120411Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-04T00:52:30.9121230Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
