2026-05-04T00:52:30.9123270Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-04T00:52:30.9124278Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-04T00:52:30.9125304Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-04T00:52:30.9126346Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
